---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/landing/Header';
import Footer from '../components/landing/Footer';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <Header client:load />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-gray">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2026
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Open Source Software</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Clearcut is open source software licensed under the MIT License. You're free to use, modify, and distribute it according to the license terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Use at Your Own Risk</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          This software is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We're not liable for any damages or losses resulting from your use of Clearcut.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Your Content</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          You retain all rights to your images. Since processing happens entirely in your browser, we never have access to your content.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">AI Model</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Clearcut uses the RMBG-1.4 model by BRIA AI. The model is subject to its own license terms. For commercial use of the model, please refer to <a href="https://huggingface.co/briaai/RMBG-1.4" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BRIA AI's licensing</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Don't use Clearcut for anything illegal or harmful. Respect copyright and intellectual property rights when processing images.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          We may update these terms occasionally. Check the "Last updated" date for the latest version.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Source Code</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          View the full source on <a href="https://github.com/MujahidAbbas/clearcut" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
